column16: Dustin Ackley singles on a line drive to left fielder Seth Smith.
Mike Zunino grounds out softly, second baseman Eric Sogard to first baseman Derek Norris.
Michael Saunders grounds out to first baseman Derek Norris.
Grant Green called out on strikes.
Kole Calhoun singles on a line drive to pitcher Pedro Figueroa.
Mark Trumbo homers (34) on a fly ball to right center field.    John Hester scores.
Mike Trout homers (24) on a fly ball to center field.   Andrew Romine scores.
Tommy Field strikes out on a foul tip.
Collin Cowgill grounds out, third baseman Alberto Callaspo to first baseman Nate Freiman.   Andrew Romine to 2nd.
Andrew Romine singles on a ground ball to center fielder Chris Young.
Eduardo Escobar grounds into a force out, third baseman Andy Parrino to second baseman Jemile Weeks.   Pedro Florimon out at 2nd.
Clete Thomas flies out to right fielder Josh Reddick.
Chris Herrmann grounds out, shortstop Eric Sogard to first baseman Daric Barton.
Mitch Moreland doubles (21) on a line drive to left fielder Yoenis Cespedes.
